However, with such a plunging neckline on her sequin-embellished gown, the Austin Powers actress, 57, was bound to stand out and turn heads at the glittering bash in Berlin.  It featured carefully layered chiffon, with the sequins beautifully arranged into love hearts and cascading down the hip-hugging, floaty skirt. The Raffaello Summer Day was held in aid of Horizons, which supports homeless children and mothers.  